        "Frown lines / glabella (11s between brows): 20–30 units. The corrugator and procerus muscles in this area are typically stronger in men — 25 units is often closer to the right dose than 15.",
        "Crow's feet (both sides): 10–16 units total (5–8 per side). More manageable for dosing, but men with deep lines at rest may need the higher end.",
